    <descript>
      <abstract>This dataset contains FCC registered cellular antenna structure locations.</abstract>
      <purpose>This dataset represents FCC registered cellular antenna structures. This mobile cellular service list mobile radiotelephone service in which common carriers are authorized to offer and provide a mobile telecommunications service for hire to the general public using cellular systems.</purpose>
    </descript>
